snippet.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Splintered Fate - Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
PC Turtle Power!? Buckle up for Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Splintered Fate on Steam! 

The adventure begins soon…
 
🐢 Wishlist now https://s.team/a//2996040 

The crime-fighting, puzzle loving, turtle brothers are back and better than ever in this rogue-like action game that will have players travel through reality-bending portals to rescue their abducted master, Splinter. 

Super Evil Megacorp is an award winning independent game studio building shared gaming experiences that push creative and technical boundaries. From our initial founding in 2012 to a global organization distributed across 11 countries. We have a shared passion and belief to make games that matter.
